            "title": "新盤開價｜啟德海灣2期首批225伙 折實平均呎價23888元 較3年前第1期高逾20％",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"477\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WwT8S0Jwv7CP.GnulH6sbg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcwMw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/3ceaa00d8315d5ecd57d430c981de9f7\" width=\"651\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">嘉華（173）、會德豐地產及中國海外（688）合作的<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"啟德海灣\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:啟德海灣;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/啟德海灣\">啟德海灣</a>2期今日開價，首批225伙，折實平均呎價23,888元，較3年前同系第1期首批折實平均呎價高逾20％。入場費560萬元，為實用面積306方呎的一房單位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">啟德海灣2期首張價單，涉及225伙，包括83伙一房、81伙兩房、61伙三房，單位實用面積由278至771方呎。以最高25%折扣計，折實560萬至2,929.8萬元，折實呎價18,032至38,000元。入場費560萬元為1C座6樓G室，實用面積306方呎，折實呎價18,301元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-14b45b63-9889-3a78-8d23-c7905552b63b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">嘉華國際發展及租務總監（香港地產）尹紫薇表示，項目首批訂價是按市價而定，項目第2期有部份屬三房海景單位，有輕微加幅，如撇除海景單位，定價較去年升2至3%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">翻查資料，項目對上一期為啟德海灣第1期於2023年10月公布首批208伙，折實均價19,798元，相隔3年推出第2期，首批折實均價已高逾20％。而且對比同區近期新盤開價，DOUBLE COAST III去年12月公布首批105伙，折實平均呎價19,399元，亦高出23％。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中原地產九龍董事劉瑛琳表示，啟德海灣第2期今日公布價單，涉及225伙，訂價與上一期貨尾造價相若，但景觀上有顯著提升，發展商誠意十足，訂價極具競爭力。市場對跑道區的海景戶需求殷切，近期成交表現理想，造價穩步上揚。參考第1期表現，單在今年首季已錄得近140伙成交，平均呎價維持約2.1萬元水平。隨著海景戶被市場快速消化，發展商轉趨惜售。除了景觀優勢，項目更具備短樓花的優點。目前跑道區租務交投活躍，平均呎租已攀升至約60元，部分優質戶更錄得70元甚至80元的高位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美聯物業高級董事布少明表示，啟德海灣第2期價單訂價貼市，擁有多項優勢，包括開揚的海景景觀、多元化的戶型選擇，以及大型住客會所等，對不同需求的買家均有吸引力，加上將來連接港鐵啟德站與跑道區的「智慧綠色運輸系統 」落成後，交通更便捷，項目升值潛力可看高一線。預計用家比例佔約6成，投資客則佔約4成，料呎租可達55元，租金回報料約4厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">啟德海灣位於承豐道15號，分2期發展，第2期由1A、1B及1C座3座相連大樓組成，樓高31層，提供1,121伙，戶型涵蓋開放式至3房，單位實用面積由258至771方呎，主打一房及兩房單位。一房提供477伙，佔約43%；兩房提供581伙，佔約52%。預計關鍵日期為今年6月底，樓花期約2個月。</p><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://lgltdclass.com/ken_freeclassreg_bmyt/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CFOCMTzEz4og89TU7pLaow--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzMw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/ae6af5ac577c6b197341c289fcb33169\" width=\"900\"/></div></a></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%A4%E9%96%8B%E5%83%B9-%E5%95%9F%E5%BE%B7%E6%B5%B7%E7%81%A32%E6%9C%9F%E9%A6%96%E6%89%B9225%E4%BC%99-%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E5%91%8E%E5%83%B923888%E5%85%83-%E8%BC%833%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E7%AC%AC1%E6%9C%9F%E9%AB%98%E9%80%BE20-055948342.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 14:13:08",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "澳新銀行:中國的「不良」通脹仍優於通縮",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CfH_FWIuK6zxDmMIwU.AYA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC290AN_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"澳新銀行\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:澳新銀行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/澳新銀行\">澳新銀行</a>分析師週三在一份報告中表示,中國可能會比市場預期更早地擺脫長期通縮週期,重返正值價格指標,儘管復甦可能伴隨挑戰。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳新銀行表示,預計中國的生產者價格指數(PPI)、消費者價格指數(CPI)和GDP平減指數將在2026年第一季度全部轉為同比正增長,其中GDP平減指數預計將上升約0.5%,這將是三年來的首次擴張。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一轉變主要由輸入性通脹推動,特別是能源價格上漲,分析師將其描述為「不良」通脹,因為它可能會擠壓本已疲弱的消費和工業盈利能力。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cbd62a4f-fc90-3d79-9b8a-7cbe2ccb21ad-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,澳新銀行表示,這種通脹仍優於通縮,後者一直是由中國經濟中供需持續失衡所驅動。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳新銀行分析師表示:「中國在管理成本方面擁有豐富的專業知識和資源,但提振消費的能力有限。」他們指出,政策制定者在應對成本上升方面比應對價格下跌更具優勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行表示,油價上漲可能會支撐可再生能源等特定板塊的需求,但不太可能解決更廣泛的經濟失衡問題,同時也會對家庭支出造成壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">預計政策制定者將依賴一系列工具來管理通脹壓力,包括行政管控、動用戰略石油儲備、財政補貼以及努力實現能源進口多元化。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳新銀行補充稱,中國可能會繼續在其再通脹策略下推進供給側改革,旨在結束通縮週期,作為建立更統一全國市場努力的一部分。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E6%96%B0%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84-%E4%B8%8D%E8%89%AF-%E9%80%9A%E8%84%B9%E4%BB%8D%E5%84%AA%E6%96%BC%E9%80%9A%E7%B8%AE-053414087.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 14:13:11",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "理財葉師傅｜港股後市仍有波動機會 過夜部署風險高｜Gary Sir",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jlgZHeFzehCaz3eHx7TRhA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bossmind_356/259e03b8c6df2451f0970c212abb27e2\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統以摧毀伊朗文明的極限施壓下，美伊達成兩星期的停火協議，為美伊中止衝突帶來曙光。環球市場避險情緒減退，恒指周三抽升3%至25,893點。不過，美伊衝突最終能否長期停火仍具有不確定性，後市波動性仍高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美伊兩國雖暫時停火，但兩國各自開出的談判條件相信難以令對方接受，談判破裂再開打的機會仍存。短期港股料波動性仍強，只宜作即市短炒，過夜部署的風險尚高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個股方面，小米（1810）周三大幅反彈6%，但要再進一步向上的難度不小，上方阻力位分別在33.3元及35.48元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f0fd7c9f-d1ec-3392-a5b3-8e30685d7b95-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">泡泡瑪特（9992）低位彈高近8%，但該股仍處下跌趨勢兼能量仍低，不宜追入。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美團（3690）有見底反彈跡象，但能量尚欠不足，待升穿90元後才追入也不遲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元下跌，黃金回升至近4,800美元，短期有力重上5,000美元水平，但若要再向上突破，則須更多利好因素。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Gary Sir 資深投資者<br/>註：專欄作家言論不代表本網立場</strong></p><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://signup.hkiei.com/garysir_bossmind\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/u_lbyPKtHpHAwJ7JKtEUSg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExMDI-/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bossmind_356/ba913bad9cf2ad999d7d1518edb55e0c\" width=\"892\"/></div></a></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%90%86%E8%B2%A1%E8%91%89%E5%B8%AB%E5%82%85-%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E5%BE%8C%E5%B8%82%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E6%B3%A2%E5%8B%95%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83-%E9%81%8E%E5%A4%9C%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E9%AB%98-gary-sir-041500301.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 12:21:24",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "領展出貨｜領展以逾15億出售新加坡零售物業權益 市場憧憬派息 股價升逾2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"639\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Y0qVWunJwsdViDt7WbLl7g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/bossmind_356/0a925d884292fb4d94c3f3c37d456af5\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">領展（823）宣佈，將出售一項<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"新加坡\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:新加坡;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/新加坡\">新加坡</a>零售物業權益，作價2.5億新加坡元（約15.4億港元），預計交易於今年第二季完成。市場憧憬將派息回饋股東，刺激股價今早曾升逾2%，暫報38.52元，暫升2.18%</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">領展表示，已與東南亞房地產投資公司Jack Investment Pte Ltd及Pangjwee Development Pte Ltd達成協議，出售其位於新加坡零售物業Swing By @ Thomson Plaza的權益。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-fc0b5bd8-c5e1-3881-8ed0-c8eb6fecbcc3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">資料顯示，領展於2022年底進軍新加坡，上述物業的收購價為1.725億新加坡元（約10.6億港元），意味持貨逾3年賬面賺45%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">集團指，是次出售作價較該物業的最新賬面估值錄得溢價。此交易屬領展持續推行資產組合優化策略的一部份，旨在於合適情況下進行資本循環，為基金單位持有人創造價值。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">領展執行董事兼首席投資總裁宋俊彥稱，在領展繼續專注發揮亞太區零售商場核心優勢、並有意增加在新加坡投資比重同時，資產循環依然是其積極優化資產組合策略中不可或缺的一環。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他又指，這次出售令領展將資產增值的成果變現，並在資金超過短期需要的情況下，讓其將資金回饋基金單位持有人。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E5%87%BA%E8%B2%A8-%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E4%BB%A5%E9%80%BE15%E5%84%84%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD%E6%AC%8A%E7%9B%8A-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%86%A7%E6%86%AC%E6%B4%BE%E6%81%AF-%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%8D%87%E9%80%BE2-032506447.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 11:37:58",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "國際｜伊朗公布霍爾木茲海峽水域安全航道圖　通知船隻守原則免觸雷",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"國際｜伊朗公布霍爾木茲海峽水域安全航道圖 通知船隻守原則免觸雷\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nvJ6N1NDpC3.YMtrx76erg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">國際｜伊朗公布<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>水域安全航道圖 通知船隻守原則免觸雷</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗港口和海事組織於當地星期三公布霍爾木茲海峽水域安全航道圖，通知往來船隻遵守航運安全原則，避免觸雷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">組織在聲明中指出，2月28日至4月8日，波斯灣及霍爾木茲海峽水域戰事不斷，霍爾木茲海峽主要航道內，可能存在各類反艦水雷，為確保海上航運安全，避免觸雷，往來船舶應按照伊朗方面公布的安全航道圖航行，直至另行通知。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另外，伊朗新聞電視台昨日報道，霍爾木茲海峽已完全關閉，一些運油輪被迫返航。伊朗塔斯尼姆通訊社就報道，仍有大量船舶在霍爾木茲海峽附近海域滯留。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0b95b642-e600-30e0-860b-ae188d454bbf-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
